  <scopecontent id="aspace_2744731c8ad951fbdf9330c42aebfa3a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Memorabilia from the 1994 Gay Games, including registration packets, photographs, ephemera, T-shirts, periodicals and newspapers. This Collection also includes some memorabilia from the 25th anniversary of the Stonewall riots since both events took place in New York City in June, 1994.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <odd id="aspace_c3972a10e9d716ace2f4d701282d184b">
